                    <CardTitle className="text-white flex items-center">
                      <Star className="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 mr-2" />
                      Why Choose Home Tuition?
                    </CardTitle>
                  </CardHeader>
                  <CardContent className="space-y-3">
                    <ul className="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
                      <li>â€¢ Comfortable learning in your own environment</li>
                      <li>â€¢ Flexible scheduling based on your availability</li>
                      <li>â€¢ Personalized attention and customized teaching</li>
                      <li>â€¢ Direct interaction with experienced astrologer</li>
                      <li>â€¢ Practical hands-on learning approach</li>
